text: Bence Stipsicz (born 3 February 1997) is a Hungarian professional ice hockey defenceman currently playing for Fehérvár AV19 of the Austrian Hockey League (EBEL). ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Fehérvár AV19 players Category:Cedar Rapids RoughRiders players Category:Hungarian ice hockey defencemen Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
